ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMarrakesh Treaty to Facilitate Access to Published Works for Persons Who Are Blind, Visually Impaired, or Otherwise Print Disabled
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to ratify, on behalf of Canada, the MARRAKESH TREATY TO FACILITATE ACCESS TO PUBLISHED WORKS FOR PERSONS WHO ARE BLIND, VISUALLY IMPAIRED, OR OTHERWISE PRINT DISABLED.
